    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_10_10798-10853",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "10798-10853",
      "markText": "霸者假借仁义，亦可与王者同功。要其优礼前代之意虽假，而于宽恤民生，使久罹水火之人倚我以图苏息，则事实不可诬也。",
      "totalCount": 110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814403&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10798&rangeEnd=10853",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c632da05c6d430c61cc5ab?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10798&rangeEnd=10853"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_10_12005-12038",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "12005-12038",
      "markText": "翌日丙辰，以孔子六十五代孙允植袭封衍圣公，其五经博士等官袭封如故。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814403&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12005&rangeEnd=12038",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c632da05c6d430c61cc5ab?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12005&rangeEnd=12038"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_8_5392-5436",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5392-5436",
      "markText": "清皇子封王，除开国八王外，例不世袭。迄光绪中叶以前，破例止一次，即世宗所特异之怡贤亲王也",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814403&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5392&rangeEnd=5436",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c632da05c6d430c61cc5ab?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5392&rangeEnd=5436"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_11_991-1035",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "991-1035",
      "markText": "明初两世有亲藩之祸，清初两世得亲贵之力，新开化之种族，淳朴有甚于汉人，此亦其不可轻量者。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814403&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=991&rangeEnd=1035",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c632da05c6d430c61cc5ab?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=991&rangeEnd=1035"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_5_878-1049",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "878-1049",
      "markText": "真正史料，皆出于史中某一朝之本身所构成，闻野记，间资参考，非作史之所应专据也。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814403&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=878&rangeEnd=1049",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c632da05c6d430c61cc5ab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=878&rangeEnd=1049"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_7_2938-3012",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2938-3012",
      "markText": "明之惠于属夷者，以建州女真所被为最厚。清世尽讳之，于清史料中固不见其事，于明史料中虽见，而清修《明史》，务尽没之。此今日始大发现，而以余为发现最多。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814403&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2938&rangeEnd=3012",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c632da05c6d430c61cc5ab?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2938&rangeEnd=3012"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_5_1101-1138",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1101-1138",
      "markText": "中国史之系统，乃国家将行一事，其动机已入史，决不待事成之后，乃由史家描写之",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814403&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1101&rangeEnd=1138",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c632da05c6d430c61cc5ab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1101&rangeEnd=1138"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814403_10_18583-18644",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "18583-18644",
      "markText": "当开国时不得已而暂行，则在历史上固为可恕，且世祖明有不得已之表示，较之明代溺爱子弟，向国民婪索庄田者，尚较有羞恶是非之心。",
